        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "In the sudden stab of fear that pierced her very heart she realized what Anne had come to mean to her. She would have admitted that she liked Anne-nay, that she was very fond of Anne.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
