        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"mr Barry, what has happened to her?\" she gasped, more white and shaken than the self-contained, sensible Marilla had been for many years.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
