    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Let us look on the bright side of things.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Mercy me, the child has gone and fainted!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "It was quite true.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "matthew, hastily summoned from the harvest field, was straightway dispatched for the doctor, who in due time came, to discover that the injury was more serious than they had supposed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "That night, when Marilla went up to the east gable, where a white faced girl was lying, a plaintive voice greeted her from the bed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"It was your own fault,\" said Marilla, twitching down the blind and lighting a lamp.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"And that is just why you should be sorry for me,\" said Anne, \"because the thought that it is all my own fault is what makes it so hard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "If I could blame it on anybody I would feel so much better.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "But what would you have done, Marilla, if you had been dared to walk a ridgepole?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"I'd have stayed on good firm ground and let them dare away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Such absurdity!\" said Marilla.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "I haven't.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "I just felt that I couldn't bear Josie Pye's scorn.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "It's not a bit nice to faint, after all. And the doctor hurt me dreadfully when he was setting my ankle.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "I won't be able to go around for six or seven weeks and I'll miss the new lady teacher.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "She won't be new any more by the time I'm able to go to school. And Gil-everybody will get ahead of me in class.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Oh, I am an afflicted mortal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000038_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000038_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "But I'll try to bear it all bravely if only you won't be cross with me, Marilla.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"There, there, I'm not cross,\" said Marilla.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"You're an unlucky child, there's no doubt about that; but as you say, you'll have the suffering of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000039_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000039_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Here now, try and eat some supper.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"Isn't it fortunate I've got such an imagination?\" said Anne.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "\"It will help me through splendidly, I expect.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "What do people who haven't any imagination do when they break their bones, do you suppose, Marilla?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "But she was not solely dependent on it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000041_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000041_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "She had many visitors and not a day passed without one or more of the schoolgirls dropping in to bring her flowers and books and tell her all the happenings in the juvenile world of Avonlea.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Why, even Superintendent Bell came to see me, and he's really a very fine man.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Not a kindred spirit, of course; but still I like him and I'm awfully sorry I ever criticized his prayers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "He could get over that if he'd take a little trouble.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "I gave him a good broad hint.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "He told me all about the time he broke his ankle when he was a boy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "When I try to imagine him as a boy I see him with gray whiskers and spectacles, just as he looks in Sunday school, only small.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Isn't that something to be proud of, Marilla?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "When a minister's wife has so many claims on her time!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "She never tells you it's your own fault and she hopes you'll be a better girl on account of it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Even Josie Pye came to see me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "I received her as politely as I could, because I think she was sorry she dared me to walk a ridgepole.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000023",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000023.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-698",
        "content": "Diana has been a faithful friend.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-698_122863_000042_000024",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/698/122863/698_122863_000042_000024.wav",
